Comment: 0,0:00:00.86,0:00:01.58,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Main script
Comment: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:32.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{title}Resound in the Blue Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.58,0:00:05.68,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A large contingent of the Roman Army has appeared at the Seize border with Nomansland?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.26,0:00:26.37,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aisha!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:30.10,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What was that gunshot?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.64,0:00:36.22,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We've secured a Roman soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.69,0:00:38.69,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is she dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.69,0:00:40.45,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, she's still breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:41.60,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:47.95,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Our troops will now reconvene with the 1st and 3rd divisions at the border-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.96,0:00:48.68,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.68,0:00:49.60,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.27,0:00:52.27,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Move and I'll shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.27,0:00:53.52,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.70,0:01:00.16,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Colonel, please have your men outside the fortress stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.95,0:01:06.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What the heck's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:07.41,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A mutiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.86,0:01:11.74,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The girls took our commanding officer hostage and barricaded themselves in!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.74,0:01:13.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.67,0:01:18.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fortunately, it missed her vital organs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.79,0:01:22.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't think she's in any immediate danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.01,0:01:24.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you, Yumina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.83,0:01:27.31,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:31.30,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We were planning on using her as a sacrifice to wage war.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.43,0:01:33.51,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She would be worthless if she had died.{lit: Her value would drop greatly if she had died.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:34.93,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.52,0:01:38.08,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}For the past month,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.38,0:01:43.74,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}we have been following the Roman soldiers who were mobilizing at the rear of our country.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.35,0:01:48.30,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That was probably to gain an upper hand in the peace talks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:50.73,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They sure underestimated us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.70,0:01:55.21,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}However, His Highness, the Archduke, decided to remain passive and take no action.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.06,0:02:00.51,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So, in order for them to make the first move, we need to give them a little push.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:06.09,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A push, like a prisoner of war being shot to death, screaming, right before their eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:07.50,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can't possibly be-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:08.88,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Peace talks are a farce!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:12.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Rome must be overthrown!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:15.49,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't you agree, Kannagi Noël--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.49,0:02:19.64,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}no, my distinguished comrade, the Witch of Helvetia?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:22.81,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did you think I wouldn't notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.81,0:02:23.69,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Enough of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.69,0:02:26.23,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Noël was used by you, wasn't she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.06,0:02:31.97,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Noël-san, you really are connected with the Invisible Reaper...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:34.46,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Invisible Reaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:40.27,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The one hailed as a rare, once in a century genius at the academy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:44.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}the Invisible Reaper, who revived the bio-weapons plant from the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:47.22,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}is that girl sitting before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.84,0:02:50.22,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your talent is wasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.22,0:02:51.92,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:03.93,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kureha-chan, throw him in the underground distillery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.89,0:03:09.28,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My comrades have already been deployed to fight the Romans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:12.87,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A little push will set the wheels in motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:18.96,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's back to the battlefield again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:21.76,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just when I thought it was finally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:23.50,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're both jinxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:27.51,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The Colonel has been locked inside the distillery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:29.83,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you, Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:40.67,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eat some if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:44.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}These pastries are popular in Treize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.02,0:03:44.70,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.09,0:03:46.95,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Naomi-san, you're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.21,0:03:49.77,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll leave when it gets dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.53,0:03:55.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is really messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.53,0:03:58.32,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The Flame Maidens were supposed to protect the city,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:04:01.94,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but instead, we're getting them involved in the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:03.73,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, regarding that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.51,0:04:10.34,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}While we were hiding, I heard about the legend of the Flame Maidens from Aisha-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.94,0:04:16.73,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And she said that the literature handed down in Rome tells a different tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:18.73,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What does it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:22.73,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The Flame Maidens protect other lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:45.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:47.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's time to change shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:48.91,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:50.84,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'd be worried with you out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:54.61,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}For starters, can you really shoot someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.53,0:05:01.65,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I believe strongly that it's the right choice, I might be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:03.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:05.75,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm a maiden of the fortress as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:09.75,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just like the Flame Maidens before us...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:10.91,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:15.29,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You believe that fairy tale the Roman made up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:16.18,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:18.87,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can sort of understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:21.80,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The Flame Maidens protect lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:26.65,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think that might actually be what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:30.81,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:41.32,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:42.73,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hear what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:46.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.71,0:05:55.74,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No matter how good her hearing is, she can't possibly hear it from this distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:57.45,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A ceasefire signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:05:59.45,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes! I heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.89,0:06:03.93,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:05.25,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Without a doubt!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:08.30,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's too soon to get excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:10.26,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She might have misheard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:15.55,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even if it's true, we don't know if the peace talks have been concluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:18.56,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Anyway, we should tell Colonel Hopkins-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:20.11,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:23.22,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When I went to bring food to the Colonel, he wasn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.95,0:06:28.42,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm glad you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:31.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Commence the strike in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:32.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:39.72,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you think that the Colonel will just listen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.32,0:06:42.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's no harm in trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:46.31,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:48.14,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:52.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The Colonel was laughing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.45,0:06:58.30,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When the Reaper that I revived killed all those people,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:00.27,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}he laughed wholeheartedly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:05.62,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He will kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:08.53,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He will fight until there's no one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:12.87,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And I had a hand in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:14.87,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:21.04,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you believe that, then save more lives than you've taken, Noël-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.12,0:07:27.50,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aisha...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.69,0:07:29.20,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ceasefire, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:30.21,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Quit joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:32.84,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I trust her ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:33.60,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:35.10,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We'll vouch for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:40.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even though she's easily teased, forgetful, acts like a kid and isn't sexy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.03,0:07:42.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Onee-chan wouldn't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.03,0:07:43.65,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Arrest this old woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:45.94,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you want a war that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:50.30,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}War is what advances civilization and science.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.91,0:07:56.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to restore it... the glory man once had.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:58.58,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:02.12,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The Romans are attacking tomorrow morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.78,0:08:07.26,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So, the war is unavoidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:10.70,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Naomi-san has been arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.43,0:08:25.32,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:25.98,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.49,0:08:28.98,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're opposing the Demon of Vingt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:32.65,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I want it to reach him. This sound that I've been given!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:33.77,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:35.15,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:37.78,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can't act according to your willful notions!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.02,0:08:39.87,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:45.51,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Someone said... that the world is already over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.37,0:08:49.12,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I like this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.95,0:08:51.58,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I like this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:53.83,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I love the people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:58.59,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Giving up... is something I can't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.08,0:09:00.37,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kanata...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:02.48,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:06.22,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stop the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:09.68,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aisha-san said the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:11.29,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:23.94,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have killed many people as a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:26.94,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm just the same, Noël.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:39.30,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm... the same as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:43.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have suffered enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:45.38,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have suffered enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.67,0:09:53.80,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So don't blame yourself any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:58.65,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:18.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Will you forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:25.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you, Aisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:30.43,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If we do this, we can never turn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:33.19,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you all fine with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:37.18,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:46.90,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then I... have nothing else to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:50.25,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:52.76,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you, Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:58.25,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have been objecting all this time, for our sakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:03.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:10.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}don't want a girl my age to be tortured!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:12.49,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But without Rio-senpai here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:18.29,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And Noël and Kanata are so lax...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:22.23,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So I thought I must do my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.59,0:11:28.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry for being such an unreliable Commander...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:30.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:35.61,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's go, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.97,0:11:36.63,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:43.90,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}May the blessings of all of the Gods be upon the Flame Maidens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.45,0:11:54.87,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Primary converter reactor output rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.87,0:11:59.31,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}FAP, FAC, DMR, ECP: all green.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:02.86,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Superconductor circuit within stable parameters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.31,0:12:05.83,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fire control system: all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:09.40,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Primary and secondary armaments: operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:11.24,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Release all joint locks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:21.25,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-Weight reduction system operational. Minus influence: approximately five.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:24.25,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Launch preparation: complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:27.54,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We'll be fine if we do as we trained.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:30.27,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's go, my dear ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:31.30,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.71,0:12:33.30,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prepare to fire main cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:34.78,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Load AP round!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.07,0:12:36.77,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}AP round loaded!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:46.95,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Target locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.39,0:12:48.80,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kana-chan, the signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:49.44,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.73,0:13:05.96,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Commence attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:11.44,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:49.04,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's Kanata-neechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:50.71,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The Takemikazuchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:50.71,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{background}They're inside that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.77,0:13:55.46,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They've advanced that far in restoring the old technology?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.74,0:13:57.30,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Signal all tanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:14:00.05,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Go all out to prevent escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:01.39,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Commence attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.39,0:14:02.73,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're not letting you through!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:04.45,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We don't want any more war!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.45,0:14:06.19,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't get in their way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:09.52,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you insist on going, you'll have to defeat us first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:10.56,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.56,0:14:11.86,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So, what will you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:14.24,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Demon of Vingt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:29.56,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:31.74,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reconvene with the forces to our rear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.86,0:14:40.45,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The Flame Maidens protect lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.43,0:14:45.51,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I leave the rest to you, Kanata-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:52.30,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A very long time ago, {or shall we go with the standard fairytale opening, "Long, long ago..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:55.56,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}before the world became as it is now,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:15:01.30,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}an angel sent by God to pass divine judgement was injured,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:06.48,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and set down its wings to rest in the far reaches of the West.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:17.44,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The ones who saved the angel were the maidens living in a fortress there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.57,0:15:22.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Despite that the angel was sent to destroy them,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:27.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}the maidens took pity on the injured angel,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:30.35,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}borrowing the strength of an enormous spider,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:33.89,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and hid the angel in the valley below.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:39.49,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To stop the blood that was pouring out,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:42.41,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}the maidens took turns embracing the angel's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:49.71,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And in gratitude, the angel bestowed upon the maidens a golden horn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:56.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But before long, the townspeople discovered the angel's existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:15:59.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and set the bottom of the valley ablaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:05.79,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The maidens were devoured by the flames, and the angel's head fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.02,0:16:08.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And they slowly succumbed. {I had tl-ed as, "and they breathed their last breath." But this didn't fit lines below}{literally, "and they just wanted to go"}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:18.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}At that moment, a host of angels appeared, covering the sky above the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.71,0:16:21.31,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}However, a miracle occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:24.66,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A glorious sound of the heavens echoed through,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:26.99,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and the angels departed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:37.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The townspeople were saved by the final maiden, who with her very last breath...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.67,0:16:40.26,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}had sounded the golden horn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:56.06,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, you remember that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:58.65,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The one you gave the caramel to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:02.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She'll be caught in this too, won't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:04.41,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All units, prepare to charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.61,0:17:07.13,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:08.51,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.25,0:17:13.18,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:24.84,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:28.72,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:33.56,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's an allied tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.96,0:17:35.66,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Which unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.14,0:17:38.85,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The 1121st Platoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.87,0:17:54.88,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's the ceasefire signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:01.58,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:03.66,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a Roman military signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:06.90,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:08.11,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We can't pull back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.11,0:18:09.39,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prepare main cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:13.41,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's useless... They're not stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.83,0:18:14.52,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.35,0:18:22.36,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kana-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:05.91,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That young lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.96,0:20:10.98,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, what the heck are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:12.34,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I ordered you to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:13.89,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fire! You will fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.89,0:20:15.29,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Both sides, lay down your arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:35.74,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I am a daughter of the royal family, second in line to succeed the throne of Helvetia,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.74,0:20:38.79,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and fiancée to the Emperor of the Holy Rome,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:41.24,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Rio Kazumiya Arkadia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.48,0:20:48.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I represent my father, the Archduke of Helvetia, and I am here to convey a message from the Roman Emperor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.46,0:20:49.70,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We have attained peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:52.48,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There will be no more fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:55.30,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Both sides are to disengage immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:57.62,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is an imperial decree!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.01,0:21:04.18,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Those who do not comply shall face the might of the First Helvetia Royal Guard,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:05.56,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}in the names of both leaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:06.92,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.07,0:21:15.06,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:17.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We don't have to fight anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.19,0:21:48.85,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:51.36,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.35,0:21:54.77,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.27,0:22:25.61,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Spring is in full bloom. {alt: it feels completely like spring.}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.41,0:22:28.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh yeah, Noël,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.01,0:22:32.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}what did Aisha write in her letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.38,0:22:38.17,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"I've recovered from my injuries and have been practising the trumpet."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.55,0:22:37.20,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Translate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.38,0:22:41.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's fine and has been practicing trumpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.00,0:22:43.20,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see. What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.42,0:22:50.57,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aw, we even got letters from Rome, but none came from the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.57,0:22:52.71,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sure she's busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.71,0:22:54.71,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Senpai is a princess, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.46,0:22:57.96,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But you know, even on the battlefield,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.96,0:23:00.76,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}she was surrounded by guards,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.14,0:23:03.18,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and we didn't get to speak with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.77,0:23:05.49,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I hear Klaus-san's bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.38,0:23:15.13,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's here! She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.13,0:23:17.44,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've been waiting for you, newbie!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.56,0:23:19.21,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm going to train her so har-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.53,0:23:42.88,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As of today, I will be under the command of the 1121st Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.42,0:23:45.39,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Lieutenant Rio Kazumiya Arkadia.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.33,0:23:49.40,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Captain Filicia Heidemann, I request your permission to begin my duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.00,0:23:51.46,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Permission granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.46,0:23:54.90,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There are no ranks here, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.45,0:23:56.73,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.20,0:24:01.59,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That Roman Emperor is a pretty understanding guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.18,0:24:07.42,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He said he would grant a single wish as a reward for stopping the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.41,0:24:10.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.83,0:24:15.18,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.18,0:24:16.18,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.18,0:24:17.95,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.41,0:24:21.54,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Welcome home, Rio.
